#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a chi-square distribution."
msgstr "从卡方分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:3 of
msgid ""
"When `df` independent random variables, each with standard normal "
"distributions (mean 0, variance 1), are squared and summed, the resulting"
" distribution is chi-square (see Notes).  This distribution is often used"
" in hypothesis testing."
msgstr ""
"当 `df` 个独立的随机变量，每个都服从标准正态分布（均值为 0，方差为 1），"
"平方并求和后，所得的分布即为卡方分布（参见注释）。此分布常用于假设检验。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:8 of
msgid "Number of degrees of freedom, should be > 0."
msgstr "自由度数，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:10 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``df`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(df).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``df`` 是标量，则返回单个值。否则"
"，抽取 ``mt.array(df).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:15 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:17 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:19 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:22 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized chi-square distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的卡方分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:25 of
msgid ""
"When `df` <= 0 or when an inappropriate `size` (e.g. ``size=-1``)     is "
"given."
msgstr "当 `df` <= 0 或者给定不合适的 `size`（例如 ``size=-1``）时。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:29 of
msgid ""
"The variable obtained by summing the squares of `df` independent, "
"standard normally distributed random variables:"
msgstr "通过对 `df` 个独立且服从标准正态分布的随机变量进行平方并求和得到的变量："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:32 of
msgid ""
"Q = \\sum_{i=0}^{\\mathtt{df}} X^2_i\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:34 of
msgid "is chi-square distributed, denoted"
msgstr "服从卡方分布，记作"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:36 of
msgid ""
"Q \\sim \\chi^2_k.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:38 of
msgid "The probability density function of the chi-squared distribution is"
msgstr "卡方分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:40 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{(1/2)^{k/2}}{\\Gamma(k/2)}\n"
"x^{k/2 - 1} e^{-x/2},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:43 of
msgid "where :math:`\\Gamma` is the gamma function,"
msgstr "其中 :math:`\\Gamma` 是伽马函数，"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:45 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\Gamma(x) = \\int_0^{-\\infty} t^{x - 1} e^{-t} dt.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:48 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.chisquare.chisquare:49 of
msgid ""
"NIST \"Engineering Statistics Handbook\" "
"http://www.itl.nist.gov/div898/handbook/eda/section3/eda3666.htm"
msgstr ""

